SONG LYRICS:

Sohni Rann wangu Lishkaake kaddiya
Jhotey bande saare jhotiya ne gaddiya
Dollara de thabbe ni
leerheya te lggey ni
Akh ne lakka di takseem maarli
Bachke rahi ni hun full jharhiye bamb bni firdi cream baahrli
Bachke rahi ni chandigarh waliye tere sehar ghumdi cream baahrli

Minti ni koi Be-hisaab pee gye 
2.5-3 kille da kmaad pee gye
baithe’an hayatt lehra-behra’n lgiyaa’n
gaddi jinne mull di shraab pee gye
Kaagza bagair koley peaa asla nange hathyaar pye ne cheer faarh lyi
Bachke rahi ni hun full jharhiye bamb bni firdi cream baahrli
Bachke rahi ni chandigarh waliye tere sehar ghumdi cream baahrli

Swa ser de gya dealer choti da sirrey lggi pyi aa gal maal aali v 
Thandi kitti hoyi aa rlaake bhasma’n garam taseero aa Imphal aali v 
Khaan te Smaan Khulla dulla chlda akh hoyi pyi aa red bean naal di
Bachke rahi ni hun full jharhiye bamb bni firdi cream baahrli
Bachke rahi ni chandigarh waliye tere sehar ghumdi cream baahrli

Saade bina gal bndi ni gerhi routa te eve ta mandeera gerhe 20 laundiyaa
Murhde flata nu lai jaayiyee raunka baad vich pariyaa ni jee laundiya
kalli- kalli hath’n vich kri firde jehri-jehri nigaa ch haseen chaarhli
Bachke rahi ni hun full jharhiye bamb bni firdi cream baahrli
Bachke rahi ni chandigarh waliye tere sehar ghumdi cream baahrli

Niggaa ch leyaati galwatti aale ne Husan te sohi aali team baahrli

About Creedence Clearwater Revival: 
Creedence Clearwater Revival’s 1968 self-titled debut album introduced the world to guitar-playing brothers John and Tom Fogerty, drummer Doug Clifford, and bassist Stu Cook, four young men out of El Cerrito in the San Francisco Bay Area. Though they emerged in a place and time where trippy psychedelic visions were the order of the day, CCR bucked the trends and instead tapped into a rich, traditional seam of American music that connected to blues, country, rockabilly, gospel, folk and R&B.    

During their short time together as a band (1968 – 1972), the band enjoyed an unparalleled period of creativity lead by singer, songwriter, arranger John Fogerty. They’ve sold close to 100 million records, releasing 14 Top 10 hits. They also managed to play over 150 tour dates around the world, including a headlining spot at Woodstock.

Creedence Clearwater Revival’s canon has become a part of the Great American Songbook. Fogerty penned songs like “Bad Moon Rising,” “Down on the Corner,” “Fortunate Son,” “Have You Ever Seen the Rain,” “Proud Mary,” “Born on the Bayou,” “Travelin’ Band” and “Up Around the Bend” have been ingrained into pop culture — not just as rock staples, but as classic standards.

With so many memorable songs that continue to grace our radio waves, television and movie screens, plus lyrics that still resonate today, Creedence Clearwater Revival is, truly, America’s greatest rock ’n’ roll band.

#ccr #creedenceclearwaterrevival #fortunateson

snippet.title: MC 張天賦 - 無名氏 Perfect Strangers (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
MC 張天賦 - 無名氏 Perfect Strangers (Official Music Video)

MC 張天賦 溫馨提示《無名氏》
不問回報的好人依然存在，請你繼續相信善良

請別忘記，
這座冰冷的小島上，
每天都有不同的溫暖故事正在發生。

例如，
黑雨之中，會有路人為你撐傘擋雨；
當你沒帶零錢坐巴士時，會有陌生人替你付費；
走在街上，會有無名氏拍拍你的肩膀，
提醒你背包的拉鏈沒拉好。

如果某天，
你發現你對這種不問回報的善意有所疑惑，
突然變得不太理解，
請容許我再次溫馨提示：
請你，繼續相信善良。

#MC張天賦 #無名氏 #PerfectStrangers 

——————

曲：陳可為 / 齊樂平
詞：黃偉文
編：Dick Wong / 周錫漢
監：周錫漢

誰於街角提醒我 扒手想過來開鎖
誰撐起傘來遮我 如果黑雨淋濕我
去坐巴士錢不夠 你來付費請我坐
跟你是好友麽 為何熱心幫我

明明不需要 待我好
為何竟普照 我路途 
其實你 不過路人
回頭就 再找不到
小恩賜 大美好
給悲劇都市 還原 樂觀指數
讓人間 接近消失的光 再望到 

掛念簡單的相處 各懷善意的偶遇
自何日失信心 懷疑另有意思

明明不需要 待我好
為何竟普照 我路途  
其實你 不過路人 
回頭就 再找不到
小恩賜 大美好
給悲劇都市 還原 樂觀指數
讓人間 接近消失的光 再望到 

願傳頌 你的好
好比旱地種 薰衣草 
無名氏 毋問回報                  
留芳於瘠土                     

明明心灰了 又碰到
如羣星普照 我路途  
無限個 親切路人 潛藏在 冷冰冰小島
心穿了 為我補
感激遇到你 證實仁慈並非 是少數
近乎哭 你就伸出雙手 抱抱 

羣星隱進人海裏
從不需要誰嘉許
如這恩我還不了
餘溫等我傳開去

MC 張天賦 - 無名氏 Perfect Strangers (Official Music Video)

MC 張天賦 溫馨提示《無名氏》
不問回報的好人依然存在，請你繼續相信善良

請別忘記，
這座冰冷的小島上，
每天都有不同的溫暖故事正在發生。

例如，
黑雨之中，會有路人為你撐傘擋雨；
當你沒帶零錢坐巴士時，會有陌生人替你付費；
走在街上，會有無名氏拍拍你的肩膀，
提醒你背包的拉鏈沒拉好。

如果某天，
你發現你對這種不問回報的善意有所疑惑，
突然變得不太理解，
請容許我再次溫馨提示：
請你，繼續相信善良。

#MC張天賦 #無名氏 #PerfectStrangers

曲：陳可為 / 齊樂平
詞：黃偉文
編：Dick Wong / 周錫漢
監：周錫漢

誰於街角提醒我 扒手想過來開鎖
誰撐起傘來遮我 如果黑雨淋濕我
去坐巴士錢不夠 你來付費請我坐
跟你是好友麽 為何熱心幫我

明明不需要 待我好
為何竟普照 我路途 
其實你 不過路人
回頭就 再找不到
小恩賜 大美好
給悲劇都市 還原 樂觀指數
讓人間 接近消失的光 再望到 

掛念簡單的相處 各懷善意的偶遇
自何日失信心 懷疑另有意思

明明不需要 待我好
為何竟普照 我路途  
其實你 不過路人 
回頭就 再找不到
小恩賜 大美好
給悲劇都市 還原 樂觀指數
讓人間 接近消失的光 再望到 

願傳頌 你的好
好比旱地種 薰衣草 
無名氏 毋問回報                  
留芳於瘠土                     

明明心灰了 又碰到
如羣星普照 我路途  
無限個 親切路人 潛藏在 冷冰冰小島
心穿了 為我補
感激遇到你 證實仁慈並非 是少數
近乎哭 你就伸出雙手 抱抱 

羣星隱進人海裏
從不需要誰嘉許
如這恩我還不了
餘溫等我傳開去

snippet.title: Lorna Shore - In Darkness (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Lorna Shore - In Darkness - Official Video. On Tour Now in Europe/UK + North American Tour this spring!

From the new album 'I Feel The Everblack Festering Within Me' - Out Now. Get it now: 
https://ifeeltheeverblackfesteringwithinme.com/
https://lornashoreband.com/

'In Darkness' is about growing up feeling distant from everyone- a song about anxiety and being an outcast (as many of us metal fans grow from). It’s a song about embracing that outlandish and ostracized feeling. Knowing that we have grown in the shadows, the darkness- of the world, but accepting that through that darkness we have become. - WILL RAMOS

LYRICS //

WE ARE ALIVE
I WATCH THE SHADOWS
FALL ON HORIZONS WE ECHO
WE ARE THE DIFFERENCE
A CONGREGATION OF LIKE MINDED HUES AND SEPARATION
AN INTROVERSION OF LIFE
AM I BROKEN, LOST, BATTERED AND TOSSED
I WAS THE ONE ON THE OUTSIDE SEARCHING FOR PEACE I WOULD NEVER FIND
BLACK ROSES LOOM IN THE DARK
NEVER TO FALL APART
WE WERE PERFECTLY SEWN OVER IMPERFECT BONES
WE MADE A HOME IN THE SHADOW OF MADNESS

WE LIVE IN DARKNESS
WE COME TO LIFE
IN DARKNESS WE WON’T DIE
WE WILL SURVIVE
BENEATH THE VALLEYS OF DARKNESS
BETWEEN MOUNTAINS OF DELIVERANCE
WE FOUND A HOME BURIED BELOW
THE SHADOWS IN BETWEEN THE RABBLE WE LET GO
WE’RE NOT MISPLACED, NAUGHT, CURSÈD AND ROT
WE ARE THE ONES BURNING INSIDE
THIS IS HOW IT FEELS TO BE ALIVE
MOONFLOWERS BLOOM IN THE DARK
NEVER TO FALL APART

WE LIVE IN DARKNESS
IN DARKNESS RAVE
EXALT THE FIGHT
IN THIS EMPTINESS WE COME TO LIFE
IN DARKNESS WE ARE ALIVE
WE WERE PERFECTLY SEWN OVER IMPERFECT BONES
WE MADE A HOME IN THE SHADOW OF MADNESS

WE LIVE IN DARKNESS
IN DARKNESS RAVE
EXALT THE FIGHT
IN THIS EMPTINESS WE COME TO LIFE
IN DARKNESS WE ARE ALIVE
WE WILL SURVIVE
IN DARKNESS WE ARE ALIVE

////

snippet.title: We Have a Pretty Dark Elder Scrolls 6 Update
snippet.description:
PCGamer's Samuel Horti recently interviewed Kurt Kuhlmann, Skyrim's co-lead designer who left shortly after Starfield's release. Kuhlmann states that he was originally slated to be The Elder Scrolls 6's lead designer and laid out his vision for the game's narrative. Kuhlmann also states that Elder Scrolls 6 was originally set to release much, much earlier and dives into how a series of changes in workplace culture and broken promises by leadership led to his depature. In the video we analyze Kurt's statements and paticularly contextualize his plans for TES 6 in the broader Elder Scrolls cosmology.

Original article: https://www.pcgamer.com/games/the-elder-scrolls/bethesdas-former-elder-scrolls-loremaster-on-why-he-left-starfields-communication-breakdowns-and-how-he-wanted-the-elder-scrolls-6-to-be-the-empire-strikes-back/

Thumbnails are currenly in A/B testing. One of my selections features a mock "Elder Scrolls 6" cover by artist Tyler Wetta, edited in photoshop.

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Spider-Man: Brand New Day, the story follows an older, emotionally scarred Peter Parker from Andrew Garfield’s universe, set after the events of No Way Home, as he struggles with a life defined by loss and unresolved guilt following Gwen Stacy’s death. Haunted by fractured memories that blur past failure with fleeting redemption, Peter is pulled back into the multiversal conflict when a desperate call for help emerges from another Spider-Man, signaling that the consequences of broken timelines are far from over. As echoes of sacrifice, second chances, and unfinished responsibility collide, the narrative positions Peter at a crossroads where personal grief and greater duty intersect, forcing him to confront whether redemption is still possible and whether one universe’s mistakes can threaten them all.

snippet.title: Knight's Path — Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2855590/Knights_Path/

Knight’s Path is a story driven action RPG set in a grounded low fantasy world inspired by the Holy Roman Empire. You play as Alryk, a young disgraced noble who has lost everything and is forced to rebuild his life from nothing. What begins as a struggle to reclaim lost status slowly grows into a deeper calling.

As Alryk, you come to realize that the people of Eranthold need you. How you respond is your choice. You may walk the knightly path, embracing duty, sacrifice, and service to others, or act out of self interest, seeking personal gain and comfort. Through discipline, hardship, and choice, your decisions shape what kind of knight Alryk becomes and what his name will come to represent.

This trailer features real gameplay footage, showcasing grounded melee combat inspired by Historical European Martial Arts, atmosphere, and the world of Eranthold.
